Package org.jcatapult.action.jcatapult

Class Summary
Countries This class is a Struts action that can be called from forms or chained in order to build a Map of countries.
Countries.LocaleComparator  
Months This class is an action that can be used from forms to build a Map of months.
States This class is a common action that provides a list of the US states in a map where the key of the map is the state code and the value of the map is the state name.
Years This class is an action that can be used from forms to build a Map of years.
